Such miniors will be prevented from entering or leaving Russia if they cannot present such a power-of-attorney. In an effort to prevent international child abduction, many goverments have initiated special procedures at entry/exit points. These often include requiring documentary evidence of relationship and permission for the child's travel from the parent(s) or legal guardian if not present. Description: Goojitsu is a provider of information. We took a concept as simple as searching the Internet.
Full Description: Goojitsu is a provider of information. We took a concept as simple as searching the Internet and turned it into a skilled trade, and when it comes to our trade our Ninja's are the best. Goojitsu aims to provide both private consumers and businesses alike information on demand. The information we provide, however, is much more specific and targeted specifically to the needs of our clients. A client can ask Goojitsu to search for anything and everything, be it a person, place, thing, or even a business. Once a request is submitted then our Ninja's go to work. We literally scour the Internet and use all available resources at our disposal to provide the client with a formatted package of information. We lay the results out and will even explain our findings to the client. The scope of what we can search for is limitless and the privacy of our clients is our top priority. Maybe a mother wants a background check on a babysitter. Perhaps a college student needs research assistance.  Or maybe a businesses wants a potential partner or employee vetted. The goal of Goojitsu is to provide the requested information as quickly and accurately as possible and, most importantly, to lay out the information in an easy-to-read and understand format. Goojitsu aims to develop a unique interface on our website. Allowing both private and business clients to register for service and receive results all through our client interface. The client will be assigned a Goojitsu staff member (Ninja) or a team of staff members depending on the project size, and through our client interface and be constantly kept in the loop on the information we've obtained thus far in the search. Our staff will also be able to request more information from the client as needed to help better our results, but in most cases only a little information is needed for us to start searching. Goojitsu not only hopes to offer affordable services but to also provide over 100 new IT jobs within our first two years.
Industry Groups: Information Technology, Internet Services, Professional Services

Description: Spam Tracking and Disposable Email
Full Description: WhySpamMe tracks websites that send spam by providing users with disposable email addresses.  By generating a new disposable email every time a user gives out their address, they can hold an individual website responsible for all mail received at that address. If the user starts to receive spam messages, the user can delete that disposable email and submit a report on the website spammed them.  All messages sent to a disposable email are forwarded to a user's personal email account. Disposable email addresses are free, and never expire. Users can generate a disposable email by using Spamfire, the firefox plug-in, or Spamfire CR the Crome plug-in.
